OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FA key ally of Andy Burnham says the
OL,7,FPrime Minister in waiting will ensure
OL,8,Fthere are "plenty of women around him
OL,9,Fand in power".
OL,11,FDoncaster Central MP Sally Jameson
OL,12,Fplayed a key role in the former
OL,13,FManchester Mayor's victory in the
OL,14,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,16,FShe was part of what Burnham hailed as
OL,17,Fa "band of strong northern power
OL,18,Fwomen" following the result.
OL,26,@pD@KOUqD@MO]yD@COUzD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
