OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FThe group also included Sheffield
OL,7,FHeeley MP Louise Haigh, who is
OL,8,Frumoured to be in line for a
OL,9,Fsignificant role in the future Prime
OL,10,FMinister's cabinet.
OL,12,FBut there has been some criticism that
OL,13,FLabour, which has never had en elected
OL,14,Ffemale leader, has again put a man in
OL,15,Fthe top job.
OL,17,FSally Jameson told ITV Calendar
OL,18,FBurnham would be "very inclusive going
OL,19,Fforward", both in his government and
OL,20,Fin his relationship with MPs.
OL,26,@zD@ROU{D@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FShe said: "I think Andy will make sure
OL,7,Fthat there are plenty of women around
OL,8,Fhim and in power and indeed that
OL,9,Facross all the job roles, in
OL,10,Fgovernment and also on the
OL,11,Fbackbenches, that voices from all
OL,12,Fdifferent backgrounds and all
OL,13,Fdifferent groups are heard."
OL,15,FJameson, a former prison officer, was
OL,16,Felected in 2024 and played a junior
OL,17,Frole in Keir Starmer's government as a
OL,18,Fparliamentary private secretary.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FBut after the local elections, where
OL,7,FLabour lost a slew of seats across the
OL,8,Fregion, she called for the Prime
OL,9,FMinister to go.
OL,11,F"It was really clear to me that the
OL,12,Fcountry had sent a clear message, and
OL,13,Fthey weren't happy with the direction,
OL,14,Fand they wanted something different"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,F"It was my belief that we needed
OL,18,Fsomeone different in order to achieve
OL,19,Fthat."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@dO]yD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FBurnham has long talked about the idea
OL,7,Fof devolution, where power is moved
OL,8,Faway from central government and given
OL,9,Fto regions and local areas.
OL,11,FThat idea, according to Jameson, can
OL,12,Fbenefit Yorkshire and the Doncaster
OL,13,Fconstituency she represents.
OL,15,F"What he's done in Manchester is to
OL,16,Fshow how that can be done and how that
OL,17,Fmodel could be used elsewhere as well,
OL,18,Fto put power and money back in the
OL,19,Fhands of local areas.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,F"Local areas, cities, towns and
OL,7,Fregions, they know what is going to
OL,8,Fserve them best", she said.
OL,10,FLabour has only been in power for just
OL,11,Fover two years and they have already
OL,12,Fchanged their leader, a pattern that
OL,13,Fhas become all too familiar in recent
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FWhen Andy Burnham is given the keys to
OL,17,FNumber 10 Downing Street, he will
OL,18,Fbecome the seventh Prime Minister in a
OL,19,Fdecade.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784301514
OL,3,CBurnham ally says new PM will have
OL,4,C'plenty of women around him'
OL,6,FBut Sally Jameson told ITV Calendar
OL,7,Fthis time will be different.
OL,9,F"Andy has come in with a plan of
OL,10,Fdelivery that he wants for this
OL,11,Fcountry to make areas like Yorkshire
OL,12,Fand my constituency Doncaster better
OL,13,Foff.
OL,15,F"I think the end result will prove
OL,16,Fthat this will be the right decision."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
